{"tid":2344022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美政黨副主席：唯有動用「叛國罪」 川普才可拯救美國","createTime":"2020-12-28T11:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T04:03:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7dffbce21466925559781e85fa5af1dafb6ed70f","tid":2344022,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cqGzeh4ywnYDRnSRrlY_zA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc4MS4yNjY3OTQ2MjU3MTk3/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/DrJu92vyn7uXjn6pcgLZXA--~B/aD00MjQ7dz01MjE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/newtalk.tw/1d4edf00dda21e534d4b11e895aa1d79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FcqGzeh4ywnYDRnSRrlY_zA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc4MS4yNjY3OTQ2MjU3MTk3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDrJu92vyn7uXjn6pcgLZXA--~B%2FaD00MjQ7dz01MjE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewtalk.tw%2F1d4edf00dda21e534d4b11e895aa1d79&h=b46991c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國南卡羅萊納州立憲黨（Constitution Party）副主席、參議員競選人布萊索（Bill Bledsoe）向媒體表示，美國總統川普唯有啟用軍事法庭，拿出中國介入本次美國總統大選的證據進行軍事法庭審判，才可「拯救美國」，軍事法庭是用來審判叛國罪（treason）。<br />\n<br />\n布萊索受《大紀元》採訪表示，川普和美國國家情報總監拉特克利夫（John Ratcliffe）曾多次透露中國干預本次美國大選。拉特克利夫曾向《CBS》記者透露，包括中國、伊朗以及俄羅斯等境外勢力干預本次美國選舉，預計明年1月將發布相關調查報告。<br />\n<br />\n布萊索指出，軍事法庭不同於戒嚴（Martial Law）和《反叛亂法》（Insurrection Act），布萊索表示，他並不認為「若使用《反叛亂法》意味有人和中國共產黨在城市發起暴動，有人要推翻政府時，該法允許軍方介入。」<br />\n<br />\n布萊索提到，目前川普提出法律訴訟逾大多遭到拒絕受理，「美國法庭有許多深層政府（Deep state）的人，包含政治人物、中情局以及聯邦調查局」。布萊索認為，既然美國的民事法庭不關注這些，「那麼，只好使用軍事法庭。」<br />\n<br />\n布萊索解釋，軍事法庭是用來審判叛國罪（treason），布萊索預計國家情報總監拉特克利夫宣布相關報告後，屆時軍事法庭將會介入，布萊索稱：「我相信資金來源將會顯示，中國共產黨精心策劃整個事件。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/美政黨副主席-唯有動用-叛國罪-川普才可拯救美國-105725471.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%BE%8E%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E5%94%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%8B%95%E7%94%A8-%E5%8F%9B%E5%9C%8B%E7%BD%AA-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%89%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%8B%AF%E6%95%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-105725471.html&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx5Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=0b08857a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/美政黨副主席-唯有動用-叛國罪-川普才可拯救美國-105725471.html</a>"},{"pid":"008be4cba6141afeb93e99e00cf376d2a3f34dd6","tid":2344022,"uid":62658,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T11:15:07.000Z","msg":"放風了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e861bf457d01d4f5cbcd57a556cb9d6330fd25a1","tid":2344022,"uid":361247,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"大家都係等内戰吧<br />\n到時想無政府就去藍州<br />\n想比trump管就去紅州"},{"pid":"b5055152f9296f2806767afdfcf271165e7e95a1","tid":2344022,"uid":70238,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:29:31.000Z","msg":"一睇到大紀元三個字即走。"},{"pid":"0bfe3ccb60b2578580f064e303303f67bed40f79","tid":2344022,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又然"},{"pid":"bd2d91381e9912a0bc00094ba69be77a673678c5","tid":2344022,"uid":294182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb55dda482a9d8f4c721d00c1d545bb4a6585d95","tid":2344022,"uid":83713,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47ANnsf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47ANnsf.png&h=df2f3787&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0af1155be90d867b157929cf4100d459ea7bbe9","tid":2344022,"uid":9050,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"入黎睇到大妓院<img src=\"/asse